你在干吗? 我们不该在这停呀
What are you doing? We don't stop here.

4
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:50,379
下车
Get out of the car.

5
00:09:30,250 --> 00:09:35,540
那些家伙在车后找到的
The boys found this on the floor, in the back of the Caddy.

6
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:37,999
恩 我看过了
Yeah, they showed me.

7
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:42,600
可能和案子没关系
Could be unrelated.

8
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:44,399
可能吧
Could be.

9
00:09:44,970 --> 00:09:48,380
死者中有戴珍珠项链的吗?
Any of those dead kids wearing pearl earrings?

10
00:09:48,380 --> 00:09:50,179
没有
No.

11
00:09:51,090 --> 00:09:54,569
可能是其他人落下的
Could be someone's missing, maybe.

12
00:09:55,650 --> 00:09:57,829
我也是这么想
That what I'm thinking.

13
00:10:35,350 --> 00:10:38,049
就剩一个包了
Just one more bag after that.

14
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:22,649
维奇斯餐馆 (日落大道)

15
00:12:23,770 --> 00:12:25,679
我只想来这
I just wanted to come here.

16
00:12:27,250 --> 00:12:29,189
来维奇斯餐馆?
To Winkie's?

17
00:12:29,820 --> 00:12:31,449
只是这间
This Winkie's.

18
00:12:32,470 --> 00:12:36,219
为什么偏认准这间?
Okay. Why this Winkie's?

19
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:42,059
有点难以启齿
It's kind of embarrassing.

20
00:12:44,920 --> 00:12:46,759
说吧
Go ahead.

21
00:12:48,190 --> 00:12:51,920
我做了个与此地有关的梦 是吗?
I had a dream about this place. Oh, boy.

22
00:12:51,920 --> 00:12:53,649
明白我的意思吗?
See what I mean?

23
00:12:55,290 --> 00:12:59,399
是的 你做了个与此地有关的梦
Okay, so you had a dream about this place.

24
00:13:00,890 --> 00:13:02,799
然后呢
Tell me.

25
00:13:09,490 --> 00:13:13,589
我是第二次做这个梦了 两次都是一样的
it's the second one I've had. But they're both the same.

26
00:13:15,470 --> 00:13:19,540
梦的开始是我来到这儿...
They start out that I'm in here but...

27
00:13:19,540 --> 00:13:22,049
当时既不是白天也不是晚上...
it's not day or night...

28
00:13:22,640 --> 00:13:25,320
半黑半白的 明白吗?
it's kind of half-night, you know?

29
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:28,280
除了这些灯光外
But it looks just like this.

30
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:30,289
周围环境就像现在这样
Except for the light.

31
00:13:31,550 --> 00:13:38,990
我说不出来的害怕...
And I'm scared like I can't tell you. Of all people...

32
00:13:38,990 --> 00:13:41,569
你就站在那边
you're standing right over there.

33
00:13:45,460 --> 00:13:47,609
站在柜台旁
By that counter.

34
00:13:49,540 --> 00:13:52,979
两次梦里都有你 而且你都是一副受惊吓的样子
You're in both dreams and you're scared.

35
00:13:55,140 --> 00:13:58,609
看到你吓成那样 我更害怕...
I get even more frightened when I see how afraid you are, and...

36
00:14:02,580 --> 00:14:05,219
然后我意识到是怎么回事了
then I realize what it is.

37
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:11,139
有一个男人...
There's a man...

38
00:14:11,870 --> 00:14:14,159
在这个地方后面
in back of this place

39
00:14:16,500 --> 00:14:18,829
就是被他吓的
He's the one who's doing it.

40
00:14:20,540 --> 00:14:23,600
我可以透过墙看见他
I can see him through the wall.

41
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:25,779
我可以看见他的脸
I can see his face.

42
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:36,639
我希望永远不会在现实中看见那张脸
I hope that I never see that face ever outside of the dream.

43
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:49,280
就是这样了
That's it.

44
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:53,279
所以...你来这看他是否存在
So...you came to see if he's out there.

45
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:59,609
为了消除这种恐惧感
To get rid of this god-awful feeling.

46
00:15:02,920 --> 00:15:04,649
好的
Right then.

47
00:15:51,730 --> 00:15:53,539
他就在这附近
It's around the back.

48
00:17:02,260 --> 00:17:05,809
丹 你没事吧
Dan! Dan, are you all right?

49
00:17:37,650 --> 00:17:40,529
还是没找到那女孩
The girl is still missing.

50
00:18:01,510 --> 00:18:03,000
说吧
Talk to me.

51
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:04,889
没什么变化
The same.

52
00:18:42,920 --> 00:18:44,939
真不敢相信
I can't believe it.

53
00:19:15,310 --> 00:19:18,429
该说再见了 贝蒂
Well, it's time to say good-bye, Betty.

54
00:19:19,110 --> 00:19:22,200
-旅途中有你做伴真不错 -谢谢
-It's been so nice traveling with you. -Thank you, Irene.

55
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:26,170
我好兴奋好紧张 和你聊天真的很开心
I was so excited and nervous. It was sure great to have you to talk to.

56
00:19:26,170 --> 00:19:30,660
-记住 我要在大荧幕上看到你 -好的
-I'll watch for you on the big screen. -Okay, Irene.

57
00:19:30,660 --> 00:19:32,810
会有那么一天吗
Won't that be the day?

58
00:19:32,810 --> 00:19:35,280
祝你好运 亲爱的贝蒂
Good luck, Betty dear.

59
00:19:35,280 --> 00:19:39,670
-保重 -我会的
-Take care of yourself and be careful. -I will.

60
00:19:39,670 --> 00:19:41,890
谢谢你 亲爱的
Thanks, again.

61
00:19:41,890 --> 00:19:45,100
贝蒂 很高兴见到你 祝你好运
Betty, it was so nice meeting you. All the luck in the world.

62
00:19:45,100 --> 00:19:46,689
谢谢
Thank you.

63
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:57,760
我的包呢?
My bags?

64
00:19:57,760 --> 00:19:59,229
要去哪?
Where to?

65
00:20:00,510 --> 00:20:02,379
哈文赫特1612号
1612, Hayvenhurst.

66
00:20:05,210 --> 00:20:06,739
知道
Got it.

67
00:21:24,500 --> 00:21:26,440
我打赌你就是贝蒂
Ten bucks says you're Betty.

68
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:29,270
是的
Yes.

69
00:21:29,270 --> 00:21:33,299
-你是莲露莉斯夫人吧? -是的 宝贝
-It is Mrs. Lenoix, isn't it? -In all my living glory, baby.

70
00:21:34,110 --> 00:21:38,600
很高兴见到你 叫我可可就行了 别人都这么叫我
Pleased to meet you. Call me Coco. Everybody else does.

71
00:21:38,600 --> 00:21:41,929
-在这等等 我要去拿钥匙 -好的 可可
-Wait there and I'll go get the key. -Okay, Coco.

72
00:21:46,560 --> 00:21:48,580
维金斯
Wilkins!

73
00:21:48,580 --> 00:21:49,830
维金斯
Wilkins!

74
00:21:49,830 --> 00:21:53,520
如果那该死的狗再在大院里拉屎的话...
If that damn dog craps in the courtyard one more time...

75
00:21:53,520 --> 00:21:58,640
-我就把它烤来做早餐 -你没养宠物吧
-I'm just gonna bank his little butt for breakfast! -You don't have any pets?

76
00:21:58,640 --> 00:22:00,550
没有 虽然是合法的
No, I don't. They're allowed.

77
00:22:00,550 --> 00:22:03,720
但我真的不喜欢这儿有宠物
I just don't like them in here for obvious reasons.

78
00:22:03,720 --> 00:22:05,870
这儿曾经住过一个男人
There was a man that lived here once that

79
00:22:05,870 --> 00:22:08,410
他养了一只袋鼠
had a prizefighting kangaroo.

80
00:22:08,410 --> 00:22:13,799
你想象不到那只袋鼠 在这院子里做了些什么
You just wouldn't believe what that kangaroo did to this courtyard.

81
00:22:14,680 --> 00:22:18,190
一起去看看你姨妈的房子吧 挺不错的
Let's go see your aunt's apartment. It's a good one.

82
00:22:18,190 --> 00:22:20,139
我等不及了
I can hardly wait.

83
00:22:27,510 --> 00:22:31,549
真难以置信! 我告诉过你
It's unbelievable! I told you.

84
00:22:32,700 --> 00:22:37,260
你姨妈事先应该交待清楚了 这是钥匙
You and your aunt probably have an understanding, so here's the key.

85
00:22:37,260 --> 00:22:39,940
需要什么尽管跟我说
And if you need anything, just give a holler.

86
00:22:39,940 --> 00:22:43,620
这儿的人和我关系很好
Everybody in this building is pretty much okay with me...

87
00:22:43,620 --> 00:22:46,230
否则他们也不会住这了
or they wouldn't be here.

88
00:22:46,230 --> 00:22:49,640
如果你愿意 迟点会介绍你们认识
If you like, later on I'll introduce you around.

89
00:22:49,640 --> 00:22:52,239
如果不愿意的话也别勉强
Well, no hard feelings if you don't.

90
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:22,370
对不起 露茜姨妈没说过这还有人
I'm sorry. My aunt Ruth didn't tell me someone was gonna be here.

91
00:24:22,370 --> 00:24:25,400
-很对不起 -没关系
-I'm so sorry. -It's okay.

92
00:24:25,400 --> 00:24:30,779
我是露茜的侄女 我叫贝蒂 她应该说过我会来吧?
I'm Ruth's niece. My name is Betty. I'm sure she told you I was coming.

93
00:24:31,450 --> 00:24:35,630
出了点意外 我才在这的
There was an accident. I came here.

94
00:24:35,630 --> 00:24:38,169
我明白 我看到衣服了
I understand. I saw the dress.

95
00:24:38,720 --> 00:24:41,189
对不起 你没事吧?
I'm sorry. Are you all right?

96
00:24:42,170 --> 00:24:44,009
发生什么事了?
What happened?

97
00:24:45,300 --> 00:24:47,069
一起车...
A car...

98
00:24:48,010 --> 00:24:50,089
车祸
a car accident.

99
00:24:52,190 --> 00:24:54,129
你没事吧?
Are you okay?

100
00:24:56,570 --> 00:24:58,479
没事
I think so.

101
00:24:59,040 --> 00:25:01,119
我只是...
I was just...

102
00:25:01,650 --> 00:25:03,640
在洗澡
taking a shower.

103
00:25:03,640 --> 00:25:07,530
不好意思 你继续洗吧
Oh, my God, I'm sorry. I'll let you get back to that.

104
00:25:07,530 --> 00:25:09,889
我去整理行李
I'm gonna get unpacked.

105
00:25:13,800 --> 00:25:15,709
你叫什么名字?
What's your name?

106
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:23,349
不好意思 我还是出去吧 稍后再谈
I'm sorry, I'll get out of here. We can talk later.

107
00:26:00,770 --> 00:26:02,299
我叫...
My name is...

108
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:04,449
丽塔
Rita.

109
00:26:07,030 --> 00:26:09,109
你是我姨妈的同事吗?
Do you work with my aunt?

110
00:26:09,610 --> 00:26:13,680
不 我...不好意思
No, I...I'm sorry...

111
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:15,819
是我多事了
it's none of my business.

112
00:26:19,520 --> 00:26:21,469
她那头红发真漂亮
She has pretty red hair.

113
00:26:22,060 --> 00:26:24,250
她正在加拿大拍电影
She's letting me stay here while she's working on a movie...

114
00:26:24,250 --> 00:26:29,540
叫我来这住 估计你都知道的吧
that's being made in Canada, but I guess you already know that.

115
00:26:29,540 --> 00:26:31,869
我一辈子也买不起这种地方
I couldn't afford a place like this in a million years.

116
00:26:32,530 --> 00:26:36,220
除非我能成为电影明星
Unless, of course, I'm discovered and become a movie star.

117
00:26:36,220 --> 00:26:39,420
当然 我更愿意做个演技派 而不是靠脸蛋
Of course, I'd rather be known as a great actress than a movie star...

118
00:26:39,420 --> 00:26:42,870
不过有些人是两者兼备的
but sometimes people end up being both. So...

119
00:26:42,870 --> 00:26:46,239
这就是我来这儿的目的
that is, I guess you'd say, the story of why I came here.

120
00:26:50,040 --> 00:26:53,860
不好意思 我太兴奋了
I'm sorry. I'm just so excited to be here.

121
00:26:53,860 --> 00:26:58,349
我刚从安大略湖的深河镇来 现在我终于来到这个...
I just came here from Deep River, Ontario, and now I'm in this...

122
00:26:59,120 --> 00:27:03,279
梦一般的地方 能体会我的感受吗?
dream place! Well, you can imagine how I feel.

123
00:27:11,640 --> 00:27:13,139
坐下吧
Sit down.

124
00:27:17,450 --> 00:27:19,529
你哪里受伤了?
Where were you hurt?

125
00:27:21,940 --> 00:27:24,100
-我们得叫个医生来 -不要
-We should call a doctor. -No.

126
00:27:24,100 --> 00:27:28,940
-可能挺严重的 -不 我想睡觉
-But this could be serious. -No, I need to sleep.

127
00:27:28,940 --> 00:27:31,370
如果是脑震荡 你不能睡觉的
If you have a concussion, you shouldn't sleep.

128
00:27:31,370 --> 00:27:33,950
我睡会就没事了
I'll be okay if I sleep.

129
00:27:33,950 --> 00:27:37,489
我只想躺下睡觉
I just need to lie down here and sleep.

130
00:28:34,870 --> 00:28:41,060
亚当 我们想提些建议...
You see, Adam, there are some suggestions that ought to be brought forward.

131
00:28:41,060 --> 00:28:44,300
你说过愿意接受意见的
And I know you said you would entertain suggestions.

132
00:28:44,300 --> 00:28:47,399
大家都希望你能这么做
And that's all anybody here is asking you to do.

133
00:28:48,440 --> 00:28:52,369
你在说什么? 思路要开放一些
What are you talking about? An open mind.

134
00:28:53,280 --> 00:28:57,959
你在重新挑选女主角 因此我们...
You're in the process of recasting your lead actress, and I'm...

135
00:28:59,160 --> 00:29:02,939
我们希望你思路能开放一些
we are asking you to keep an open mind.

136
00:29:13,390 --> 00:29:15,459
上次的是什么?
What was it the last time?

137
00:29:17,390 --> 00:29:22,599
好的 试试下一位 他不会喜欢的
Okay, let's try the next one. He's not gonna like it.

138
00:29:23,340 --> 00:29:24,889
走着瞧吧
We'll see.

139
00:29:32,700 --> 00:29:36,099
卡氏兄弟 我给你们引见一下
Castigliani brothers! Let me introduce you around.

140
00:29:37,850 --> 00:29:43,690
请坐 这是达比先生 你知道的
Please take a seat. This is Mr. Darby, whom you know.

141
00:29:43,690 --> 00:29:47,170
这是导演亚当·克什尔
And this is the director, Adam Kesher.

142
00:29:47,170 --> 00:29:50,779
经理人罗伯特·斯密斯
And his manager, Robert Smith.

143
00:30:25,340 --> 00:30:27,449
她很漂亮
She's very pretty.

144
00:30:28,860 --> 00:30:32,229
先生们 想喝点什么吗?
May I offer you gentlemen anything?

145
00:30:34,490 --> 00:30:37,380
蒸馏咖啡 什么都不要
Espresso. Nothing.

146
00:30:37,380 --> 00:30:40,679
这相是拿来做什么的 一杯蒸馏咖啡
What's the photo for? One espresso.

147
00:30:42,320 --> 00:30:44,620
就这些
No, that's it.

148
00:30:44,620 --> 00:30:47,300
相信这次的咖啡你会满意的
I think you're going to enjoy your espresso this time.

149
00:30:47,300 --> 00:30:49,590
我之前做过一些调查...
I've done quite a bit of research...

150
00:30:49,590 --> 00:30:51,330
知道你很挑剔
knowing how hard you are to please.

151
00:30:51,330 --> 00:30:53,630
这咖啡重点推荐给你试试
This one comes highly recommended.

152
00:30:53,630 --> 00:30:57,729
这相是拿来做什么的? 推荐给你啊
What's the photo for? It's a recommendation.

153
00:30:58,740 --> 00:31:01,559
向你推荐的 亚当
A recommendation to you, Adam.

154
00:31:03,060 --> 00:31:06,179
这不是推荐 就要这个女孩
It's not a recommendation. This is the girl.

155
00:31:06,890 --> 00:31:10,779
什么女孩 为什么? 这是怎么一回事 雷恩?
What girl? For what? What is this, Ray?

156
00:31:11,310 --> 00:31:15,520
我们很乐意把她列为候选
We'd be happy to put her on the list for considerations.

157
00:31:15,520 --> 00:31:19,929
你应该知道 许多人对这个角色有兴趣
You'd be pleased to know, there's quite a bit of interest in this role.

158
00:31:20,800 --> 00:31:25,289
兴趣? 有六名顶尖的女演员争夺这个角色呢
Interest? There's six of the top actresses that want this thing.

159
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:27,789
就要这个女孩子
This is the girl.

160
00:31:28,390 --> 00:31:31,380
-瑞恩 这事你来处理 -别急 亚当
-Ray, take care of this. -Hold on, hold on, Adam.

161
00:31:31,380 --> 00:31:32,880
别急?
Hold on?

162
00:31:32,880 --> 00:31:35,449
没门 没门
There's no way! There's no way!

163
00:31:50,550 --> 00:31:52,499
餐巾
Napkin.

164
00:31:53,510 --> 00:31:55,350
对不起?
Pardon?

165
00:31:55,350 --> 00:31:56,849
餐巾
Napkin.

166
00:31:57,370 --> 00:31:59,279
好的
Of course.

167
00:31:59,810 --> 00:32:01,359
失陪
Excuse me.

168
00:32:18,320 --> 00:32:20,119
还需要什么吗?
Is that all, sir?

169
00:33:17,540 --> 00:33:21,090
狗屎 对不起 这可是别人重点推荐的
Shit. Sorry. That was highly recommended.

170
00:33:21,090 --> 00:33:23,910
这是公认最好的蒸馏咖啡之一
That is considered one of the finest espressos in the world!

171
00:33:23,910 --> 00:33:27,249
发生什么事了? 这个女孩是不可能演我的电影
What's going on here? There is no way that girl is in my movie!

172
00:33:31,700 --> 00:33:36,109
-就要这女孩 -这女孩不能演我的电影
-This is the girl. -Hey, that girl is not in my film!

173
00:33:39,070 --> 00:33:41,359
这电影已经不是你的了
It's no longer your film.

174
00:33:46,660 --> 00:33:48,429
就要这个女孩
This is the girl.

175
00:34:27,540 --> 00:34:30,459
卡氏兄弟上了那辆轿车没有?
Castigliani brothers get out of that limo?

176
00:34:31,130 --> 00:34:33,150
-是那两个穿黑西服的人吗? -是的
-The two guys in dark suits? -Yeah.

177
00:34:33,150 --> 00:34:35,989
把车门开着
Yes. Leave that door open.

178
00:34:46,190 --> 00:34:48,140
卡氏兄弟
