362
00:57:51,280 --> 00:57:52,969
亚当·克什尔
Adam Kesher?

363
00:57:58,240 --> 00:58:01,909
滚开 他再也不会回来的了
Get out of here! He's never coming back! Ever!

364
00:58:03,560 --> 00:58:06,310
估计你听不懂英语吧!
Bastard. I guess you don't understand English.

365
00:58:06,310 --> 00:58:08,570
她叫你离开 门在那
She said leave. Here's the door.

366
00:58:08,570 --> 00:58:10,450
杰里
Gene!

367
00:58:10,450 --> 00:58:11,799
滚开
Get out!

368
00:58:12,500 --> 00:58:13,999
滚开
Get out!

369
00:58:18,240 --> 00:58:19,869
亚当·克什尔
Adam Kesher?

370
00:58:42,560 --> 00:58:45,730
-什么事? 科基 -很抱歉 克什尔先生...
-Yeah, what is it, Cookie? -I'm sorry, Mr. Kesher...

371
00:58:45,730 --> 00:58:49,239
你的信用卡似乎有点问题
but there seems to be some problem with your credit cards.

372
00:58:50,150 --> 00:58:52,439
什么? 我给你现金吧 科基
What? I pay you cash, Cookie.

373
00:58:54,500 --> 00:58:58,569
银行的两个家伙来过这
Listen, two guys from your bank came by.

374
00:58:59,230 --> 00:59:01,029
银行?
My bank?

375
00:59:01,980 --> 00:59:04,789
-他们怎么知道我在这 -我不知道
-How'd they know I was here? -I don't know.

376
00:59:06,260 --> 00:59:08,420
他们说了些什么?
What'd they say?

377
00:59:08,420 --> 00:59:12,310
他们说你的帐户已经没钱了
They said to tell you that you're maxed out at your bank...

378
00:59:12,310 --> 00:59:15,569
你的信用卡被取消了
and that your line of credit has been canceled.

379
00:59:17,360 --> 00:59:19,369
真难以置信
That's unbelievable.

380
00:59:21,010 --> 00:59:22,739
我...
Well, look...

381
00:59:25,220 --> 00:59:30,119
我不知道发生了什么事 一群胡说八道的家伙
I don't know what's going on. That is so much baloney.

382
00:59:32,600 --> 00:59:38,399
-我有大把现金 科基 -我知道 不要担心
-I got enough cash for you, Cookie. -I know, I know. Don't worry.

383
00:59:39,210 --> 00:59:44,209
我很抱歉 不过我有义务提醒你...
But I'm sorry, it's my duty to inform you...

384
00:59:45,540 --> 00:59:50,480
小心点 不管你躲在哪...
listen, man, whoever you're hiding from...

385
00:59:50,480 --> 00:59:53,149
他们都能找到你
they know where you are.

386
00:59:54,270 --> 00:59:56,079
好的
Right.

387
00:59:57,090 --> 00:59:59,069
我很抱歉
I'm sorry.

388
01:00:22,660 --> 01:00:24,060
喂
Hello?

389
01:00:24,060 --> 01:00:28,020
-有人冻结了我的银行帐户 -我知道了 你在哪? 亚当
-Someone maybe shut off my money. -I know. Where are you, Adam?

390
01:00:28,020 --> 01:00:32,580
-你知道了是什么意思? -有人打电话找过你...
-Sorry, what do you mean you know? -Somebody called...

391
01:00:32,580 --> 01:00:36,779
他们说你已破产了 我不信 所以我打了几个电话
they told me you were as good as broke. So I made a few calls.

392
01:00:37,380 --> 01:00:39,470
-然后呢? -你确实破产了
-And? -You're broke.

393
01:00:39,470 --> 01:00:40,819
我没破产
I'm not broke!

394
01:00:41,350 --> 01:00:43,639
但你确实破产了 你在哪?
I know, but you're broke. Where are you?

395
01:00:45,140 --> 01:00:51,679
我在市区 科基这儿 你认识一个叫"牛仔"的人吗?
I'm at Cookie's, downtown. Do you know somebody called "The Cowboy"?

396
01:00:52,690 --> 01:00:54,979
-牛仔? -是的
-"The cowboy"? -Yeah.

397
01:00:55,580 --> 01:01:00,030
牛仔 这个人想见你
"The Cowboy". This guy, the Cowboy, wants to see you.

398
01:01:00,030 --> 01:01:03,059
杰森觉得应该去见他
Jason said he thought it would be a good idea.

399
01:01:03,970 --> 01:01:07,380
杰森认为我该去见牛仔吗?
Jason thought it would be a good idea for me to go see the Cowboy.

400
01:01:07,380 --> 01:01:11,100
我是不是要带上 高顶宽边呢帽和左轮手枪?
Should I wear my 1O-gallon hat and my six-shooters?

401
01:01:11,100 --> 01:01:14,329
某些迹象表明 他与所发生的事有联系
Something tells me that this guy is connected to what's happening.

402
01:01:15,520 --> 01:01:19,350
亚当 你应该去见他 马上去
Adam, I think you should do it, and you should do it right away.

403
01:01:19,350 --> 01:01:24,249
出了什么事? 辛西娅 真是怪异的一天
What's going on, Cynthia? It's been a very strange day.

404
01:01:25,640 --> 01:01:28,239
而且越来越奇怪
And getting stranger.

405
01:01:29,850 --> 01:01:33,259
我到哪和这位牛仔碰头? 要不要我骑着马去?
Where do I meet this Cowboy? Do you have to ride out to the range?

406
01:01:34,030 --> 01:01:38,900
你真搞笑 如果要找他的话...
Sort of, funny boy. If I tell him the meeting's on...

407
01:01:38,900 --> 01:01:44,470
到比奇伍德峡谷的顶上 那里有个围栏...
you'll go to the top of the Beachwood Canyon, there's a corral up there...

408
01:01:44,470 --> 01:01:48,220
-他在那等你 -你在戏弄我?
-where he'll be. -You've gotta be kidding me.

409
01:01:48,220 --> 01:01:50,690
你去不去?
Will you meet with him?

410
01:01:50,690 --> 01:01:52,120
当然去
Yeah.

411
01:01:52,120 --> 01:01:56,500
-今天真不是什么吉日 -什么时候?
-Sure. This has been that kind of a day. -When?

412
01:01:56,500 --> 01:02:00,249
我马上致电他 然后再通知你
I'll call him right away and then I'll call you back.

413
01:02:01,130 --> 01:02:05,690
如果你愿意 可以来我这里
You know, you could stay at my place, if you wanted.

414
01:02:05,690 --> 01:02:11,050
-我觉得不妥 -只是让你落落脚而已
-I don't think that'd be a good idea. -I was just offering a place to stay.

415
01:02:11,050 --> 01:02:14,560
非常感激 我自己会找地方的
Yes, and I appreciate the offer, Cynthia. I'll find a place.

416
01:02:14,560 --> 01:02:17,760
快去给牛仔打电话 然后答复我
Just go on and give that cowboy a yodel and get on back to me.

417
01:02:17,760 --> 01:02:21,520
好 我怕你什么地方可能会疏忽
Okay. But you don't know what you're missing.

418
01:02:21,520 --> 01:02:24,479
别管了 小亲亲 我等你电话
Just get along, little doggie. And call me back.

419
01:02:36,590 --> 01:02:40,689
大概就在这附近了 塞丽亚泊尼塔 不是很远
It's right about here. Sierra Bonita. It's not too far away.

420
01:02:42,120 --> 01:02:44,339
有什么问题吗?
What's wrong with that?

421
01:02:45,150 --> 01:02:47,509
我不能肯定是这儿
I'm not sure about this.

422
01:02:48,910 --> 01:02:51,969
我知道你有点害怕
I know you're afraid of something.

423
01:02:52,590 --> 01:02:55,579
我保证一定小心行事
We'll be careful. I promise.

424
01:02:56,250 --> 01:03:02,099
等明天我们去了 就知道是不是那了
Tomorrow. We'll go over there.and we'll find out.

425
01:03:15,310 --> 01:03:17,529
没事的
It'll be okay.

426
01:03:19,800 --> 01:03:22,299
可能是可可
It's probably Coco.

427
01:03:25,890 --> 01:03:30,299
-什么事? 需要帮忙吗? -有人要倒霉了
-Yes, may I help you? -Someone is in trouble!

428
01:03:32,090 --> 01:03:34,409
你是谁?
Who are you?

429
01:03:35,150 --> 01:03:38,380
你在露茜的家里做什么?
What are you doing in Ruth's apartment?

430
01:03:38,380 --> 01:03:42,940
她让我呆在这的 我是她的侄女 我叫贝蒂
She's letting me stay here. I'm her niece. My name's Betty.

431
01:03:42,940 --> 01:03:46,569
不 不是的 她不是这样说的
No, it's not! That's not what she said.

432
01:03:47,220 --> 01:03:51,249
有人倒霉了 大事不好了
Someone is in trouble! Something bad is happening!

433
01:03:52,230 --> 01:03:55,750
抱歉我不认识你 而且...
I'm sorry, but I don't know who you are and...

434
01:03:55,750 --> 01:03:59,149
露易斯 你在干什么? 露易斯
Louise? What are you doing, Louise?

435
01:03:59,820 --> 01:04:04,650
我下午3点一直在找你
I've been trying to get hold of you since 3 o'clock this afternoon.

436
01:04:04,650 --> 01:04:08,100
那人在我房间 她不肯走
That one is in my room and she won't leave!

437
01:04:08,100 --> 01:04:11,159
我要你赶她走 马上赶她走
I want you to get her out. I want you to get her out now.

438
01:04:11,920 --> 01:04:15,330
这位是露易斯·波尼尔 她没有恶意的
This is Louise Bonner. I'm sure she meant well.

439
01:04:15,330 --> 01:04:18,500
露易斯 这位是贝蒂 露茜的侄女
Louise, this is Betty, this is Ruth's niece.

440
01:04:18,500 --> 01:04:23,960
正好我要来看贝蒂 贝蒂是个演员
I was on my way over here to see Betty. Betty is a young actress.

441
01:04:23,960 --> 01:04:28,210
我来给她送明天试镜台词
I was delivering some faxed pages of a scene for a big audition tomorrow.

442
01:04:28,210 --> 01:04:31,240
-给你 甜心 -谢谢
-Well, here they are, honey. -Thank you.

443
01:04:31,240 --> 01:04:33,840
走吧 露易斯 我带你回家
Come along now, Louise. I'll take you home.

444
01:04:33,840 --> 01:04:36,070
-我很抱歉 这种事时有发生 -没关系
-I'm sorry. It happens sometimes. -Come on.

445
01:04:36,070 --> 01:04:39,450
不 她说了有人要倒霉
No, she said it was someone else who was in trouble.

446
01:04:39,450 --> 01:04:43,339
住口 我带你回家 快点
Stop it, Louise! I'm taking you home. Come on.

447
01:04:44,420 --> 01:04:46,709
-晚安 贝蒂 -晚安
-Good night, Betty. -Good night.

448
01:04:47,760 --> 01:04:49,529
晚安
Good night.

449
01:05:28,540 --> 01:05:30,559
牛仔...
Cowboy...

450
01:06:37,850 --> 01:06:41,039
您好 您好
Howdy. Howdy to you.

451
01:06:43,630 --> 01:06:45,909
很美的夜晚
Beautiful evening.

452
01:06:49,300 --> 01:06:55,179
谢谢你从旅馆大老远跑来见我
Thank you for coming all the way up here to see me from that nice hotel downtown.

453
01:06:56,740 --> 01:07:00,050
不要紧 你想怎么样?
No problem. What's on your mind?

454
01:07:00,050 --> 01:07:03,869
来了个直肠直肚的人
Well, now. Here's a man who wants to get right down to it.

455
01:07:04,430 --> 01:07:07,430
很好奇 对吗?
Kind of anxious to get to it, are you?

456
01:07:07,430 --> 01:07:09,259
随你怎么说吧
Whatever.

457
01:07:10,730 --> 01:07:13,410
一个人的态度...
A man's attitude...

458
01:07:13,410 --> 01:07:18,489
态度决定人生
a man's attitude goes some ways the way his life will be.

459
01:07:19,190 --> 01:07:21,719
你同意吗?
Is that something you might agree with?

460
01:07:22,560 --> 01:07:24,480
当然
Sure!

461
01:07:24,480 --> 01:07:28,510
你是为了讨我欢心...
Did you answer because that's what you thought I wanted to hear...

462
01:07:28,510 --> 01:07:30,770
而言不由衷...
or did you think about what I said...

463
01:07:30,770 --> 01:07:35,009
还是确实这么认为的?
and answered 'cause you truly believe that to be right?

464
01:07:35,780 --> 01:07:39,499
真心同意您的观点
I agree with what you said. Truly.

465
01:07:41,590 --> 01:07:44,329
我的什么观点?
What'd I say?

466
01:07:46,220 --> 01:07:50,149
态度很大程度上决定人生
That a man's attitude determines to a large extent how his life will be.

467
01:07:51,750 --> 01:07:54,400
根据我的观点...
So since you agree...

468
01:07:54,400 --> 01:07:59,790
你一定是个不在乎自己过的好不好的人
you must be a person who does not care about the good life.

469
01:07:59,790 --> 01:08:01,699
怎么讲?
How's that?

470
01:08:03,230 --> 01:08:05,810
停下来...
Well, stop for a little second...

471
01:08:05,810 --> 01:08:09,669
反省一下吧 拜托你这么做吧
and think about it. Can you do that for me?

472
01:08:11,900 --> 01:08:15,089
好的 我正在反省
Okay. I'm thinking.

473
01:08:18,510 --> 01:08:24,139
你根本没在反省 你真的太自以为是了
No, you're not. You're too busy being a smart aleck to be thinking.

474
01:08:24,910 --> 01:08:29,400
现在 我希望你反省 不要再自以为是了
Now, I want you to think and stop being a smart aleck.

475
01:08:29,400 --> 01:08:31,840
拜托你尝试一下
Can you try that for me?

476
01:08:31,840 --> 01:08:35,509
到底怎么回事? 你到底要我怎么做?
Look, where's this going? What do you want me to do?

477
01:08:36,460 --> 01:08:41,709
假定有一辆双座车 一辆双座车需要几个司机?
There's sometimes a buggy. How many drivers does a buggy have?

478
01:08:42,520 --> 01:08:43,869
一个
One.

479
01:08:44,570 --> 01:08:48,050
假设我已经是那个唯一的司机了
So let's just say I'm driving this buggy.

480
01:08:48,050 --> 01:08:52,699
如果你态度端正的话 你可以一起乘我的车
And if you fix your attitude, you can ride along with me.

481
01:08:55,010 --> 01:08:57,439
我希望你明天回去上班
I want you to go back to work tomorrow.

482
01:08:58,420 --> 01:09:04,289
无论如何女主角得重选 多点女孩来试镜
You were recasting the lead actress. Audition many girls for the part.

483
01:09:05,200 --> 01:09:10,670
当试到那个女孩时 你得说
When you see the girl that was shown to you earlier today, you will say:

484
01:09:10,670 --> 01:09:13,970
就是她了
"This is the girl."

485
01:09:13,970 --> 01:09:17,609
其他角色人选仍然由你定
The rest of the cast can stay. That's up to you.

486
01:09:18,530 --> 01:09:21,829
但女主角不由你定
But that lead girl is not up to you.

487
01:09:23,780 --> 01:09:28,299
表现出色的话 你还能再见我一次
Now, you will see me one more time if you do good.

488
01:09:29,320 --> 01:09:34,359
如果干的不好 你还会再见我两次
You'll see me two more times if you do bad.

489
01:09:34,990 --> 01:09:36,579
晚安
Good night.

490
01:10:02,610 --> 01:10:06,650
-你还没走 -我又回来了 这不正如你所愿吗?
-You're still here? -I thought that's what you wanted.

491
01:10:06,650 --> 01:10:10,930
-没人想看见你 -真的吗?
-Nobody wants you here! -Really?

492
01:10:10,930 --> 01:10:14,170
我父母就在楼上 他们以为你已经走了
My parents are right upstairs. They think you've left!

493
01:10:14,170 --> 01:10:18,690
-那又怎样? -很吃惊了 我要叫他们下来 叫我爸下来
-So? -Surprise. I can call them. I can call my dad.

494
01:10:18,690 --> 01:10:22,439
你不会的 你威胁我是没有用的
But you won't. If you're trying to blackmail me...

495
01:10:23,140 --> 01:10:26,030
你玩的游戏很危险
it's not going to work! You're playing a dangerous game here.

496
01:10:26,030 --> 01:10:28,680
你知道我想怎么样的 也不是很难满足的
You know what I want. It's not that difficult.

497
01:10:28,680 --> 01:10:32,220
出去 否则我把父亲叫下来
Get out! Get out before I call my dad!

498
01:10:32,220 --> 01:10:35,460
他很信任你 把你当最好的朋友
He trusts you! You're his best friend.

499
01:10:35,460 --> 01:10:37,820
一切都将结束
This will be the end of everything.

500
01:10:37,820 --> 01:10:40,890
你呢? 你父亲会怎么看你?
What about you? What will your dad think about you?

501
01:10:40,890 --> 01:10:44,779
不要说了 你一开始就这样说
Stop! Just stop it! That's what you said from the beginning.

502
01:10:45,620 --> 01:10:49,060
如果我把实情告诉他们 你就要去坐牢了
If I tell what happened, they'll arrest you and put you in jail.

503
01:10:49,060 --> 01:10:51,499
请马上离开这 免得我...
Get out of here before...

504
01:10:52,370 --> 01:10:55,880
免得你什么? 免得...
Before what? Before...

505
01:10:55,880 --> 01:11:00,469
-我宰了你 -那坐牢的就是你了
-I kill you. -Then they'd put you in jail.

506
01:11:04,090 --> 01:11:07,710
然后我会哭啊哭 接着很动情地说...
Then I cry, cry, cry, and then I say with big emotion...

507
01:11:07,710 --> 01:11:10,699
我恨你 我恨我们俩个
"I hate you! I hate us both!"

508
01:11:13,770 --> 01:11:17,479
好蹩脚的剧本 不过你真的很棒
Such a lame scene. But you are really good.

509
01:11:18,670 --> 01:11:20,929
谢谢你 亲爱的
Thank you, darling.

510
01:11:35,720 --> 01:11:38,349
你是谁?
Hi, there. Who are you?

511
01:11:41,530 --> 01:11:43,369
贝蒂
Betty?

512
01:11:50,190 --> 01:11:53,179
贝蒂 能到外面聊几句吗?
Betty, can I see you outside for a minute?

513
01:12:07,310 --> 01:12:09,400
什么事? 可可
What is it, Coco?

514
01:12:09,400 --> 01:12:10,859
你姨妈打电话给我
Your aunt called.

515
01:12:12,390 --> 01:12:14,100
我就担心会这样
I was afraid of that.

516
01:12:14,100 --> 01:12:16,979
她想弄清楚 到底是谁在她家里
She wants to know who's staying in her apartment.

517
01:12:17,930 --> 01:12:21,020
她不过呆一两个晚上就会走的
It's just for a night or two. Until she finds her own place.

518
01:12:21,020 --> 01:12:23,600
我向姨妈解释过的 但当时飞机正在起飞
I tried to explain that to aunt Ruth but the connection was bad...

519
01:12:23,600 --> 01:12:26,900
电话线路不是很好 她可能有点误会
and her plane was leaving, and she got it all mixed up.

520
01:12:26,900 --> 01:12:28,960
我说过这是我的朋友丽塔...
I kept telling her that it was my friend Rita...

521
01:12:28,960 --> 01:12:31,239
可她说不认识什么丽塔
and she kept saying she didn't know any Ritas.

522
01:12:32,500 --> 01:12:36,780
看着我 甜心 她人很好的
Look at me straight, sweetie. Coco, she's very nice.

523
01:12:36,780 --> 01:12:38,800
甜心 你是个好孩子...
Honey, you're a good kid...

524
01:12:38,800 --> 01:12:41,959
你的话听起来不错...
but what you're telling me is a load of horse puckey.

525
01:12:42,490 --> 01:12:45,100
但我却总觉的不是很踏实
Even though it comes from a good place.

526
01:12:45,100 --> 01:12:47,529
不过 我相信你会处理好这事的
I'm gonna trust you to sort this thing out.

527
01:12:48,300 --> 01:12:51,489
-谢谢 -别让我失望
-Thank you. -Don't make me out to be a sucker.

528
01:12:52,060 --> 01:12:55,659
露易斯·波尼尔说过这里要出事 记得吗? 就是昨晚
Louise Bonner said there is trouble in there, remember last night?

529
01:12:56,270 --> 01:13:00,100
她说的不一定对...
Well, sometimes she's wrong...

530
01:13:00,100 --> 01:13:04,369
但如果真有什么麻烦 就得马上解决掉
but if there is trouble, get rid of it.

531
01:13:13,980 --> 01:13:16,240
没事吧?
Is everything all right?

532
01:13:16,240 --> 01:13:21,670
-我在这给你添麻烦了吧 -没 一切都挺好的
-Is it bad for you that I'm here? -No, no, everything is A-Okay.

533
01:13:21,670 --> 01:13:26,879
我去把三文治弄好 还有一个小时就要试镜了
Now, I've gotta fix that sandwich. And my audition is in one hour!

534
01:13:46,790 --> 01:13:49,640
两小时后应该能回来
I hope I'm back in a couple of hours.

535
01:13:49,640 --> 01:13:52,880
-别把可乐都喝光了 -祝你好运
-And don't drink all the Coke. -Good luck.

536
01:13:52,880 --> 01:13:56,769
等我回来后会叫车在外面等着 你准备好
When I get back, I'll keep the cab waiting, so be ready to go.

537
01:14:29,100 --> 01:14:32,160
贝蒂·艾姆斯 给你介绍一下...
Betty Elms, I would like you to meet...

538
01:14:32,160 --> 01:14:34,339
杰克·土特曼 我的助手
Jack Tutman, my assistant.

539
01:14:35,430 --> 01:14:38,740
伍迪·卡特滋 他会和
Woody Katz, who we have cast in the part of Chuck...

540
01:14:38,740 --> 01:14:41,059
你一起表演
and will do the scene with you.

541
01:14:41,800 --> 01:14:44,100
鲍勃·保波克 我们的导演
Bob Rooker, our director...

542
01:14:44,100 --> 01:14:46,109
还有朱丽叶·卡文迪
and Julie Chadwick.

543
01:14:46,670 --> 01:14:50,920
以及让人惊喜的嘉宾 里尼·詹姆斯
Now, our surprise guest, Lynne James.

544
01:14:50,920 --> 01:14:54,190
唉 我们请不起她演戏
Alas, we can't afford her to cast our show but...

545
01:14:54,190 --> 01:14:58,349
不过挑选演员 她也是最有眼光的
well, as casting agents go, she is the best.

546
01:14:58,920 --> 01:15:02,500
谢谢 沃里 你好 贝蒂
Why, thank you, Wally. Hello, Betty.

547
01:15:02,500 --> 01:15:06,289
幸会 这是我的助手 尼奇
Very pleased to meet you. This is my assistant, Nikki.

548
01:15:07,090 --> 01:15:12,519
还有可爱的马莎·约翰逊 以前你见过的
And the ever lovely Martha. Martha Johnson, whom you met out front.

549
01:15:14,890 --> 01:15:16,169
你好
Hi.

550
01:15:16,840 --> 01:15:20,479
可以开始了吗?
So, shall we give it a go?

551
01:15:21,260 --> 01:15:25,220
要不要先来杯水或是咖啡?
Would you like a water, a coffee before we begin?

552
01:15:25,220 --> 01:15:27,310
不要了
No, I'm fine.

553
01:15:27,310 --> 01:15:30,299
好的 那么大家各就各位
Well then, let's everyone take a seat.

554
01:15:33,360 --> 01:15:39,700
贝蒂 到伍迪那边去 准备开始了
Betty, why don't you join Woody over there and we'll play the scene.

555
01:15:39,700 --> 01:15:46,270
鲍勃 有什么要交待贝蒂的?
Bob, do you have anything you wish to say? Something to Betty before we begin?

556
01:15:46,270 --> 01:15:55,319
注意 两个人之间的不是争论
No. It's not a contest. The two of them. with themselves.

557
01:15:55,980 --> 01:15:59,910
所以不要试图去演...
So don't play it for real...

558
01:15:59,910 --> 01:16:02,829
要自然一点
until it gets real.

559
01:16:07,880 --> 01:16:09,609
好的
Okay.

560
01:16:10,250 --> 01:16:12,720
告诉我哪受伤了 宝贝
Just tell me where it hurts, baby.

561
01:16:12,720 --> 01:16:14,000
什么?
What?

562
01:16:14,000 --> 01:16:18,040
我看应该演得亲热点 就像和其他女孩试镜一样
I wanna play this one nice and close like we did with that other girl...

563
01:16:18,040 --> 01:16:21,690
黑头发那个叫什么名字? 感觉挺好的 你认为怎样
what's her name? With the black hair. It felt good, what do you think?

564
01:16:21,690 --> 01:16:26,080
很好 伍迪 说那句台词别太快了
That's good, Woody. Just don't rush that line again. I told you...

565
01:16:26,080 --> 01:16:28,849
你说的是那句台词吧? "免得什么?"
the line where you say: "Before what?"

566
01:16:29,800 --> 01:16:35,739
演戏是相互影响的 我只是配合而已 她们都说的很快
Bobby, acting is reacting. I just play off them. They all say:

567
01:16:36,440 --> 01:16:39,650
"他们会逮捕你" 或者"你会去坐牢" 都说的很快
"They're gonna arrest you", like that, and: "They'll put you in jail."

568
01:16:39,650 --> 01:16:43,230
她们说的很快 我也自然说得快
They say it the same way. So when they say it, I just react.

569
01:16:43,230 --> 01:16:44,760
-你叫什么名字? -贝蒂
-What's your name? -Betty.

570
01:16:44,760 --> 01:16:50,020
听着 如果你能慢一点 我也会慢一点的 好吗?
Betty, look. You don't rush it, I don't rush it, okay?

571
01:16:50,020 --> 01:16:55,749
我们亲热一点 就像是在电影里 好吗?
Now, we're gonna play this nice and close just like in the movies, okay?

572
01:16:58,510 --> 01:17:01,349
父亲最好的朋友上班去了
Dad's best friend goes to work.

573
01:17:02,510 --> 01:17:04,039
鲍勃?
Bob?

574
01:17:08,700 --> 01:17:10,429
开始
action!

575
01:17:14,370 --> 01:17:16,319
你还没走
You're still here.

576
01:17:17,920 --> 01:17:19,800
我回来了
I came back.

577
01:17:19,800 --> 01:17:23,280
-这不正如你所愿吗? -没人想看见你
-I thought that's what you wanted. -Nobody wants you here.

578
01:17:23,280 --> 01:17:24,980
真的吗?
Really?

579
01:17:24,980 --> 01:17:29,300
我父母就在楼上 他们以为你已经走了
My parents are right upstairs. They think you've left.

580
01:17:29,300 --> 01:17:31,029
那又怎样?很惊讶吧
So, surprise!

581
01:17:31,630 --> 01:17:36,489
-我要叫他们下来 我要叫我父亲下来 -你不会的
-I can call them, I can call my dad. -But you won't.

582
01:17:52,680 --> 01:17:55,669
你会玩死自己的
You're playing a dangerous game here.

583
01:17:57,030 --> 01:18:00,160
你恐吓我是没有用的
If you're trying to blackmail me...

584
01:18:00,160 --> 01:18:02,589
你知道我想怎么样的
it's not gonna work.

585
01:18:04,020 --> 01:18:08,439
也不是很难满足的
You know what I want. It's not that difficult.

586
01:18:11,400 --> 01:18:13,169
出去
Get out.

587
01:18:15,120 --> 01:18:17,759
要不我把父亲叫下来
Get out before I call my dad.

588
01:18:18,640 --> 01:18:25,149
他很信任你 把你当最好的朋友
He trusts you. You're his.best friend.

589
01:18:29,040 --> 01:18:31,849
一切都将结束
This will be the end of everything.

590
01:18:34,190 --> 01:18:37,939
你呢? 你父亲会怎么看你?
What about you? What'll your dad think about you?

591
01:18:40,970 --> 01:18:42,989
别说了
Stop it.

592
01:18:44,450 --> 01:18:47,269
你从一开始就这么说
That's what you said from the beginning.

593
01:18:48,660 --> 01:18:53,009
如果我把实情告诉他们 他们会把你送进监狱
If I tell them what happened, they will arrest you and put you in jail.

594
01:19:00,180 --> 01:19:02,510
请马上离开这
So get out of here...

595
01:19:02,510 --> 01:19:04,309
免得我...
before...

596
01:19:07,730 --> 01:19:09,979
免得你什么?
Before what?

597
01:19:27,980 --> 01:19:30,029
免得...
Before...

598
01:19:30,660 --> 01:19:33,399
我宰了你
I kill you.

599
01:19:47,880 --> 01:19:50,759
那你就要去坐牢了
Well, then they'd put you in jail.

600
01:19:59,300 --> 01:20:01,729
我恨你
I hate you.

601
01:20:02,710 --> 01:20:04,889
我恨我们俩个
I hate us both.

602
01:20:21,040 --> 01:20:23,439
我要把她带到那边 演的很好
I'm gonna take her over there. Yeah, big time.

603
01:20:27,480 --> 01:20:29,949
就是这样了
Well, there it was.

604
01:20:30,610 --> 01:20:35,509
对 就这样 不错 宝贝 你演戏挺有一套
Yeah, there it was, all right. Baby, you got a way with you. Really.

605
01:20:36,450 --> 01:20:37,669
鲍勃?
Bob?

606
01:20:39,450 --> 01:20:42,079
真的很好
Very good. Really.

607
01:20:42,650 --> 01:20:48,659
略有点造作 不过还是挺动情的
I mean, it was forced maybe, but still humanistic.

608
01:20:50,890 --> 01:20:53,469
是的 非常好
Very good. Really!

609
01:20:53,990 --> 01:20:55,759
真的
Really.

610
01:21:01,160 --> 01:21:06,550
谢谢 贝蒂 我是真心的
Oh, I thank you, Betty. And I really mean that, sincerely.

611
01:21:06,550 --> 01:21:08,400
我是说...
I mean, it was...

612
01:21:08,400 --> 01:21:10,800
太优秀了
extraordinary.

613
01:21:10,800 --> 01:21:12,880
你的姨妈会为你骄傲的
You've done your aunt proud today.

614
01:21:12,880 --> 01:21:16,850
一有机会我就会告诉她
I'm going to tell her that first chance I get.

615
01:21:16,850 --> 01:21:21,189
现在 你和我 很快又要谈谈了
Now, you and I are going to speak again very soon.

616
01:21:21,860 --> 01:21:25,380
谢谢 布朗先生
Thank you, Mr. Brown. Thank you, Wally.

617
01:21:25,380 --> 01:21:29,380
你们肯定有不少话要谈 我们带贝蒂出去了
I'm sure you all have a lot to talk about. We'll walk Betty out.

618
01:21:29,380 --> 01:21:33,030
你能来是我们的荣幸 里尼
Yes, indeed. And it was our pleasure, Lynne.

619
01:21:33,030 --> 01:21:37,660
别把自己当外人 我们很高兴你能来
Don't you be a stranger around here. We'd love to have you here.

620
01:21:37,660 --> 01:21:40,680
走吧 贝蒂 再次感谢 布朗先生
Come on, Betty. Thank you again, Mr. Brown.

621
01:21:40,680 --> 01:21:43,909
很高兴见到大家
And it was nice meeting all of you.

622
01:21:44,480 --> 01:21:45,689
再见
Bye.

623
01:21:47,330 --> 01:21:48,959
再见
Bye!

624
01:21:53,420 --> 01:21:56,339
她真是太棒了 你究竟是从哪发掘她的?
She's a slam-dunk! Where the hell did you find her?

625
01:21:56,970 --> 01:21:59,049
天哪 真的太烂了
God, that was awful!

626
01:22:00,030 --> 01:22:04,620
不是说你 你演技一流 但可怜的沃里
Not you, Betty. You were stellar, and I mean that. But poor Wally.

627
01:22:04,620 --> 01:22:09,150
他永远演不好戏 他已经是20年前的人物了
He'll never get that picture made. Wally's days were up 2O years ago.

628
01:22:09,150 --> 01:22:12,490
伍迪·卡特滋做这些只是兴趣
You know Woody Katz is only doing it for a favor.

629
01:22:12,490 --> 01:22:14,710
至于演技 我听说非常烂
And the cast they have so far is terrible.

630
01:22:14,710 --> 01:22:19,410
是的 很烂 沃里这个可怜的蠢老头
Oh, God, terrible! That poor old fool Wally.

631
01:22:19,410 --> 01:22:23,240
他很好 他看起来很和蔼
He was very nice and he seems so sweet.

632
01:22:23,240 --> 01:22:26,090
而且沃里...布朗先生是我姨妈的密友
And Wally...Mr. Brown is a very close friend of my aunt's.

633
01:22:26,090 --> 01:22:29,400
别误会了 我爱沃里
Don't get me wrong, I love Wally.

634
01:22:29,400 --> 01:22:32,810
本应如此 我和他结婚10年了
I ought to, I was married to him for 1O years.

635
01:22:32,810 --> 01:22:38,539
我喜欢演员 所有的演员 我们只是有点油罢了
And I love actors. All actors. We just get a little catty sometimes.

636
01:22:39,350 --> 01:22:44,290
我们给你介绍一位出类拔萃的导演
We want to take you across and introduce you to a director who's a head above the rest.

637
01:22:44,290 --> 01:22:46,970
他那部电影很适合你
He's got a project you will kill for.

638
01:22:46,970 --> 01:22:49,639
一炮而红
Knock right out of the park!

639
01:24:42,730 --> 01:24:47,630
停 非常感谢 卡罗 我很快就回来
Cut it! Thank you very much, Carol. Checking the gate?

640
01:24:47,630 --> 01:24:50,169
谢谢 我们会给你个结果的
Checking the gate! Thank you. We'll tell you what happens next!

641
01:24:50,870 --> 01:24:53,690
非常感谢你的光临 我知道你很忙
Thank you very much for coming in. I know how busy you are.

642
01:24:53,690 --> 01:24:56,780
和我开玩笑? 我喜欢这个剧本 告诉我在哪签字
Are you kidding me? I loved the script. Just show me where to sign.

643
01:24:56,780 --> 01:24:59,950
我喜欢你 不过我要见完...
I love you, but there's no way they're gonna let me cast this thing...

644
01:24:59,950 --> 01:25:02,520
所有人选后再决定 我会尽快通知你的
until I've seen everyone. I'll let you know as soon as I can.

645
01:25:02,520 --> 01:25:05,839
我知道你会的 因为我的经纪人会日夜骚扰你 我也会
I know you will. Because my manager is gonna be bugging you. And me!

646
01:25:07,470 --> 01:25:10,740
这是我的荣幸 离开这儿 你对我太冷谈了
My pleasure. Now get outta here. You're so cruel to me.

647
01:25:10,740 --> 01:25:13,549
我演定了这角色 再会
I'm the girl who's playing this part. I'll see you later.

648
01:25:15,480 --> 01:25:17,780
汉克 汉克在哪
Hank? Where's Hank?

649
01:25:17,780 --> 01:25:20,249
-下一位是谁 汉克 -是卡米拉·罗丝
-Who's next, Hank? -Camilla Rhodes.

650
01:25:21,610 --> 01:25:23,999
-她准备好了吗? -都准备好了
-Is she ready? -All ready.

651
01:25:24,910 --> 01:25:27,789
-带她进来 -下一位卡米拉·罗丝
-Bring her in. -Camilla Rhodes, next.

652
01:25:34,060 --> 01:25:37,669
西尔维亚诺兹故事 卡米拉·罗丝
"Sylvia North Story". Camilla Rhodes, take one.

653
01:25:38,270 --> 01:25:40,739
好了 开始了
Okay, here we go. Let's lock it up, please.

654
01:25:41,470 --> 01:25:44,050
请放音乐
Roll sound, please. That's fit.

655
01:25:44,050 --> 01:25:45,919
开始
Playback and action.

656
01:26:17,630 --> 01:26:21,899
叫杰森来这 辛迪 亚当想见杰森
Get Jason over here. Cindy, Adam wants to see Jason.

657
01:27:00,940 --> 01:27:04,379
怎么没有告诉我 你有事找我吗?
Why haven't you told me? Did you want to tell something?

658
01:27:15,210 --> 01:27:17,319
就是这个女孩了
This is the girl.

659
01:27:22,380 --> 01:27:24,919
真有眼光 亚当
Excellent choice, Adam.

660
01:27:36,330 --> 01:27:38,269
天啊
Oh, my goodness.

661
01:27:47,880 --> 01:27:50,110
我得走了
I have to be somewhere.

662
01:27:50,110 --> 01:27:52,399
我约了朋友
I promised a friend.

663
01:27:53,270 --> 01:27:56,879
对不起 我得走了 现在?
I'm sorry, I must go. Now?

664
01:28:21,280 --> 01:28:23,359
应该就在这附近了
Should be around here.

665
01:28:24,240 --> 01:28:26,990
2-5-9-0 就是它了
259O. That's it.

666
01:28:26,990 --> 01:28:29,799
在那边 眼熟吗?
Up there! Does it look familiar?

667
01:28:38,750 --> 01:28:41,640
-别停车 -怎么了? 你看到什么了?
-Don't stop! -What is it? What do you see?

668
01:28:41,640 --> 01:28:45,039
坐在那辆车前面的人 你认识他们吗?
Those men, in front, in the car. Do you know them?

669
01:28:46,440 --> 01:28:49,109
绕到他们后面去
Keep going. Go around to the back.

670
01:29:37,860 --> 01:29:40,609
西恩 12号
Selwyn, number 12.

671
01:30:04,270 --> 01:30:06,669
你吓死我了
Now you got me scared.

672
01:30:31,000 --> 01:30:32,600
看到没?
You see?

673
01:30:32,600 --> 01:30:35,619
都说过没什么可怕的了
I told you there was nothing to be afraid of.

674
01:31:37,450 --> 01:31:38,839
贝蒂 等等
Betty, wait. Wait!

675
01:31:41,380 --> 01:31:42,879
别
Don't.

676
01:32:09,360 --> 01:32:12,040
没人在家
No one's home.

677
01:32:12,040 --> 01:32:13,659
什么事?
Yes?

678
01:32:15,030 --> 01:32:16,869
戴安妮
Diane?

679
01:32:18,610 --> 01:32:20,729
她在17号
Number 17.

680
01:32:22,510 --> 01:32:25,049
但那上面写着是12号
But it said number 12.

681
01:32:26,820 --> 01:32:29,020
我和她换了房子 她在17号
I switched apartments with her.

682
01:32:29,020 --> 01:32:32,869
在左边的最尽头
She's in 17. It's down at the end, on the left.

683
01:32:37,510 --> 01:32:40,419
不过她好几天没露面了
But she hasn't been around for a few days.

684
01:32:42,550 --> 01:32:45,060
我们可以给她留个条
We'll leave her a note.

685
01:32:45,060 --> 01:32:47,039
我和你们一起去
I'll go with you.

686
01:32:49,060 --> 01:32:51,529
我还有东西在她那里
She still got some of my stuff.

687
01:32:56,960 --> 01:32:59,869
你们去吧 我要接个电话
You go ahead. I gotta get that.

688
01:33:14,880 --> 01:33:18,519
-估计你不是戴安妮·西恩 -我也觉得不是
-Guess you're not Diane Selwyn. -Guess I'm not.

689
01:33:56,140 --> 01:33:58,879
可能还是没人在家
There's still no one home, I guess.

690
01:34:28,290 --> 01:34:30,889
你在干什么? 来吧 帮我一把
What are you doing? Come on, help me in.

691
01:34:32,050 --> 01:34:34,679
我要把前门打开
Come on, I'll open the front door.

692
01:34:35,460 --> 01:34:37,049
别
No!

